---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";

const frontmatter = {
    title: "VMware to Proxmox Migration",
    status: "Completed",
    statusType: "completed",
    origin: "Client Migration Project",
    date: "2025.07",
    techStack: ["VMware ESXi", "Proxmox VE", "Linux", "PowerShell", "Bash"],
};
---

<ProjectLayout frontmatter={frontmatter}>
    <h2>// Overview</h2>
    <p>
        Executed a seamless infrastructure migration from VMware ESXi to Proxmox VE with zero downtime for an online
        platform. This project demonstrated the viability of open-source virtualization for production workloads.
    </p>

    <h2>// Technical Implementation</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Assessment and inventory of existing VMware environment</li>
        <li>Parallel Proxmox cluster deployment</li>
        <li>Disk conversion from VMDK to QCOW2 format</li>
        <li>Live migration using shared storage</li>
        <li>Network cutover with minimal interruption</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>// Results</h2>
    <p>
        Successfully migrated 25+ virtual machines with less than 5 minutes total downtime. Annual licensing costs
        reduced by over 80%.
    </p>

    <h2>// Status</h2>
    <p>Migration completed. Client environment running stable on Proxmox VE.</p>
</ProjectLayout>
